ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This was a useful survey course which also encouraged interesting, independent work with particular manuscripts. I would definitely recommend this to another student, as long as said student had a strong familiarity with Latin.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Although I work on medieval history, my focus has been primarily social and economic, and I was less familiar with legal history. This course remedied that and greatly increased my familiarity with medieval law. I now feel much more comfortable looking into legal texts to find information relevant to my main research interests.
